      <img src="http://timedotcom.files.wordpress.com/2014/11/bilss-cosby-1.jpg?w=280" itemprop="image" alt="Actor Bill Cosby in New York in 2011." srcset="http://timedotcom.files.wordpress.com/2014/11/bilss-cosby-1.jpg?w=1100 800w, http://timedotcom.files.wordpress.com/2014/11/bilss-cosby-1.jpg?w=1100 800w 2x"/>
