      <figcaption class="image-caption">
        <span class="caption">From Left: Afton Elaine Burton and Charles Manson, imprisoned for life for association with a series of murders in the 1960s in Corcoran, Calif. on Aug. 14, 2011.</span>
        <span class="credit">Manson Direct/Polaris</span>
